{"tid":1222384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[輕輕鬆鬆做好功課]通識老師教你睇逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:24:16.000Z","uid":11331,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"05aa1b1e3a201765dd5e3f05aa2c66a418191ab1","tid":1222384,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"首先多謝咁多位連日留守現場既義士, 唱歌既傳教士, 或者做文宣, 搞不合作運動既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果冇你地咁多位一點一滴既付出, 逃犯條例肯定一早過咗, 香港都已經玩完<br />\n<br />\nProud to be a hongkonger!<br />\n希望我地繼續團結落去, 惡法撤回之前 堅持不割席 堅持不放棄 目標一致不撤不散<br />\n<br />\n入正題先, 雖然黑警死全家, 但我地最緊要係撤回條惡法<br />\n出咗咁多日現場 (係呀屌你 唔係發夢 摘鳩我名囉屌你死黑警)<br />\n成日聽到大家嗌「撤回!撤回!撤回!」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者各出奇謀總之要阻佢開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係做得好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我發現其實部份巴打們對條條例認識不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有好多巴打唔知點說服屋企人<br />\n甚至有CCTVB以外既記者訪問既時候都唔係幾夠膽答 又或者講唔贏支持條例啲柒頭<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家做好啲功課! 暫時搵到條比較易服用既YOUTUBE片講逃犯條例<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KINTINGLS/videos/299770780978119/UzpfSTE2OTUxNTA5Mjg6MTAyMDUzNjYzMjM3OTI5NzI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKINTINGLS%2Fvideos%2F299770780978119%2FUzpfSTE2OTUxNTA5Mjg6MTAyMDUzNjYzMjM3OTI5NzI%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=e7f15b29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KINTINGLS/videos/299770780978119/UzpfSTE2OTUxNTA5Mjg6MTAyMDUzNjYzMjM3OTI5NzI/</a><br />\n結論同我地諗法係一致 全程貼地廣東話 <br />\n各位請安心服用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有更好既片歡迎SHARE<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為冇用 雖然你未必有梁天琦咁好口才 咁有魄力(<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1631007887184323/videos/1704174829867628/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1631007887184323%2Fvideos%2F1704174829867628%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=42dd18ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1631007887184323/videos/1704174829867628/</a>)<br />\n但肯定你做完功課之後 唔多唔少你都答到啲野 <br />\n冇人屌到你係盲反, 因為你一定理解條條文多過佢<br />\n特別係學生身份/00後既比較冇示威經驗既同路人, <br />\n包裝完真係成個會唔同哂, 我剩係諗到都出哂水要拖拖地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然有啲人係唔講道理 講多兩句都唔得就請一野BLOCK落去<br />\n再次真心感謝各位香港義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b94bfc35f1e1614d6abf598a0ddfb78535d9bb","tid":1222384,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"39935efd1d35b3829b2938dc33b76fbd6be50cec","tid":1222384,"uid":149574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efddea4420e2c5b346b41c2bfcfe5b84e65ce463","tid":1222384,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b94bfc35f1e1614d6abf598a0ddfb78535d9bb","tid":1222384,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e751955f45de3d91d13855ace9508b65dd9b7bea","tid":1222384,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efddea4420e2c5b346b41c2bfcfe5b84e65ce463","tid":1222384,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b94bfc35f1e1614d6abf598a0ddfb78535d9bb","tid":1222